def f( a=1, b=10):
b_first = a
b_prev = b_first
q = 2
ls = []
ls.append(b_first)
for i in range(a, b):
    b_cur = b_prev*q
    if b_cur <= b:
        ls.append(b_cur)
        b_prev = b_cur
return ls
